name: TezHeadz // 080
description:
The TEZHEADZ are Pixel Based Entities Time Traveling back from the Future on the Tezos Blockchain to save Crypto! The only way to escape the Evil AI overlords was to embed the last fragments of the human Soul into Pixels on the Blockchain. Help save humanity by Rescuing that Special 1 of 1 Tezhead & HODL all the way thru the Apocalypse!
Each one is Hand Generated by the Humans :)
